<recipe lang="en-uk" xmlns:lxslt="http://xml.apache.org/xslt">
<title><![CDATA[Autumn squash soup with walnut pesto]]></title>
<description><![CDATA[There is an abundance of squashes and pumpkins on the market at the moment; the deep orange-fleshed varieties offer the best flavour and colour.]]></description>
<source/>
<img></img>
<cuisine>
<style>European</style>
